{"tid":1783164,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欣宜託汪明荃幫老竇開IG　秋官竟然咁答！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-12-14T14:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T16:28:49.000Z","uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6f3c58763b857544e436e95434a3bb863a2012","tid":1783164,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T14:33:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191214/photo/bkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_01b.jpg?20191214110308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20191214110308&h=302608ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人汪明荃（Liza姐）早前玩Instagram（ig）創出「汪阿Tag」掀起一股熱潮，玩ig玩到出神入化！最近佢就與老拍檔鄭少秋（秋官）齊齊到雲頂登台，Liza姐於ig上載合照，秋官穿着風褸配頸巾，與紅色打扮及拿住一盆聖誕花嘅Liza姐並肩合照，甚有氣氛。<br />\n不過最有趣嘅係秋官女兒鄭欣宜竟然留言「Liza姐快啲教我爸開ig啦」，反應非常快嘅Liza姐即回覆欣宜：「<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你爸說：Don't make me trouble！（唔好令我麻煩）</span></span></strong>」非常搞笑，不過唔少秋官粉絲都留言希望佢開個帳戶呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191214/photo/bkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_02b.jpg?20191214110308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20191214110308&h=6838a185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191214/photo/bkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_03p.jpg?20191214110308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191214%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20191214110308&h=05f99107&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191214/photo/bkn-20191214013212029-1214_00862_001_04b.jpg?20191214110308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2